    <abstract id="aspace_46e73b320b3d18fd5543360cb7de1517">Consists primarily of three diaries that William Dundas Bathurst (1859-1940) kept while serving as an officer of the Association Internationale du Congo (AIC) from December 1883 to September 1886.</abstract>
